Tactics for determining combat targets for friendly or hostile actions.

Party member:
    Hitpoints below a certain threshold
        Prefer lowest health?
    Mana below a certain threshold
    Afflicted by condition
        Sleep
        Poison
        ...etc.
Self:
    Hitpoints below a certain threshold
    Mana below a certain threshold
Enemy:
    Lowest health
    Highest health
    Most armor
    Lowest armor
    Melee
    Ranged